 Suki Waterhouse 分享引人注目的新单曲“OMG” https://www.nme.com/news/music/suki-waterhouse-shares-striking-new-single-omg-3569920?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=suki-waterhouse-shares-striking-new-single-omgAnagricel Duran Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:25:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3569920 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="苏琪·沃特豪斯。图片来源：玛德琳·沃特豪斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌曲标志着她 2024 年的首张专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suki-waterhouse-shares-striking-new-single-omg-3569920">Suki Waterhouse 分享的引人注目的新单曲“OMG”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="苏琪·沃特豪斯。图片来源：玛德琳·沃特豪斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse.-Credit-Madeleine-Waterhouse-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/suki-waterhouse">Suki Waterhouse</a>分享了她 2024 年的第一首单曲《OMG》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/suki-waterhouse-her-debut-album-i-cant-let-go-3207459">苏琪·沃特豪斯谈她的首张专辑：“陷入焦虑让我感到自由”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手、模特兼演员因在艾美奖提名电视剧<em>《黛西·琼斯与六人组</em>》中饰演凯伦·西尔科而闻名，过去一周她一直在社交媒体上调侃这首歌。</p><p>这首歌由 Waterhouse 与 Natalie Findlay 共同创作，并由 Jules Apollinaire 制作，是一首合成低俗歌曲，带有时髦的低音线和突出的鼓声，同时 Waterhouse 唱着： <em>“Oh my God / Take me back the way of the I was / Oh my God / You知道我只是想玩你的游戏/所以你不能忘记我的名字/你和我不一样/你总是过得很轻松”</em>指的是过去的恋情。</p><p> “我们开始了一半的歌曲，然后把它放在一边，”沃特豪斯告诉<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/suki-waterhouse-omg-video-1234939039/"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>。 “我们当时想，‘这不起作用。’然后两个月过去了，我们回到录音室，突然这副充满能量的副歌就出来了。” </p><p><iframe title="Suki Waterhouse - OMG（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9Vf7DA-AB08?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她继续说道：“当我尝试创作一首歌时，这是一种非常焦虑的状态，因为你总是感觉自己处于某件事的边缘。这实际上是违背理智并进入歌曲的本能。这就是我觉得写作如此迷人的地方。这确实是最乏味、最微妙的过程，所以取决于你那天能否摆脱自己的束缚。”</p><p>由埃米莉·理查德·弗鲁赞 (Émilie Richard-Froozan) 执导的《OMG》随附视频中，沃特豪斯 (Waterhouse) 展现了她内心的伊迪丝·琵雅芙 (Edith Piaf)，她穿着鲜艳的红色礼服，眉毛在温室中舞动。她还让粉丝们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/suki-waterhouse-expecting-first-child-with-robert-pattinson-3544217">一睹她逐渐长大的肚子</a>。</p><p> 《OMG》是这位歌手 2023 年发行的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-suki-waterhouses-optimistic-new-song-to-love-3408621">To Love</a> 》之后的作品，并将收录在她即将于今年晚些时候通过 SupPop 发行的第二张专辑中。它将继她的首张唱片“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/suki-waterhouse-i-cant-let-go-review-3218855">I Can&#39;t Let Go</a> ”之后。 </p><figure id="attachment_3569957" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3569957" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3569957" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="苏琪·沃特豪斯《OMG》封面艺术。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Suki-Waterhouse-OMG-Cover-Art.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3569957" class="wp-caption-text">苏琪·沃特豪斯《OMG》封面艺术。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p><em>NME</em>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/suki-waterhouse-i-cant-let-go-review-3218855">对该唱片的四星级评论</a>中分享道：“由次流行音乐支持的《I Can&#39;t Let Go》为我们呈现了这位英国音乐家和演员生活的亲密写照，充满了强烈而有力的情感。 。这张唱片非但没有将事情封闭起来，也没有回避这些内心的感觉，而是让其创作者——进而延伸到我们——感受一切。”</p><p>去年，沃特豪斯宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/suki-waterhouse-expecting-first-child-with-robert-pattinson-3544217">她即将迎来与演员罗伯特·帕丁森的第一个孩子</a>。</p><p>她于 11 月 19 日在墨西哥城举行的科罗纳首都音乐节 (Corona Capital Festival) 上表演时宣布了这一消息。 “我今天特别闪亮，因为我认为这可能会分散你对正在发生的其他事情的注意力，”沃特豪斯一边说一边打开她的夹克。 “我不确定这是否有效，”她开玩笑说，引起了人群的欢呼。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/suki-waterhouse-shares-striking-new-single-omg-3569920">Suki Waterhouse 分享的引人注目的新单曲“OMG”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
